---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="ABOUT | Sosun Fihaara">
<main>

<section class="page-hero">
  <img id="brands-hero-img" class="page-hero__img" src="/placeholder.jpg" alt="Sosun Fihaara warehouse stacked with FMCG goods" loading="eager">
  <div class="container page-hero__inner">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p class="crumbs"><a href="index.html">Home</a> &nbsp;/&nbsp; <span>About Us</span></p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STORY -->
<section class="section bg-cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split">
      <div class="split__media"><img src="/placeholder.jpg" alt="A well-stocked retail store in the Maldives" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div>
        <span class="kicker">Rooted in trust, grown for tomorrow</span>
        <h2>Supplying the Maldives, one shelf at a time</h2>
        <p>For four decades, Sosun Fihaara has been a backbone of FMCG distribution in the Maldives — moving the food and grocery products that island communities depend on every single day.</p>
        <p>We bridge global manufacturers and local shelves. Our wholesale arm supplies retailers, cafés and institutions at volume; our retail focus ensures end customers always find the authentic, quality brands they trust. From Malé to the furthest atoll, dependable supply is our promise.</p>
        <a href="products.html" class="textlink mt-3">See What We Stock <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M5 12h14M13 6l6 6-6 6"></path></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- VALUES -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head center">
      <span class="eyebrow">What drives us</span>
      <h2>The values behind <span class="accent">every delivery</span></h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-3">
      <article class="card"><div class="card__body">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--green-soft);display:grid;place-items:center;color:var(--green);margin-bottom:16px"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l8 4v6c0 5-3.5 8-8 10-4.5-2-8-5-8-10V6z"></path><path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>Dependability</h3><p>Shelves stay full because we plan, warehouse and deliver with precision. When we commit, you can count on it.</p>
      </div></article>
      <article class="card"><div class="card__body">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--green-soft);display:grid;place-items:center;color:var(--green);margin-bottom:16px"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l2.4 7.4H22l-6 4.4 2.3 7.2-6.3-4.6L5.7 21 8 14 2 9.6h7.6z"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>Genuine Quality</h3><p>Every brand we carry is authentic and quality-assured — from sourcing standards to cold-chain handling.</p>
      </div></article>
      <article class="card"><div class="card__body">
        <div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:12px;background:var(--green-soft);display:grid;place-items:center;color:var(--green);margin-bottom:16px"><svg width="26" height="26" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path></svg></div>
        <h3>Partnership</h3><p>We grow with the retailers we serve — fair terms, responsive trade support and a relationship built to last.</p>
      </div></article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS -->
<section class="section--tight bg-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stats" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.06)">
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat__num">40+</div><div class="stat__label">Years in distribution</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat__num">25+</div><div class="stat__label">Brands represented</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat__num">15</div><div class="stat__label">Product categories</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="stat__num">100%</div><div class="stat__label">Authentic stock</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROCESS TIMELINE (unique) -->
<section class="section bg-cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head center">
      <span class="eyebrow">From sourcing to shelf</span>
      <h2>How we keep the Maldives <span class="accent">supplied</span></h2>
      <p>A disciplined four-step pipeline that turns global manufacturing into reliable local availability.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
      <article class="tl-step"><h3>Source</h3><p>We partner directly with trusted global manufacturers and negotiate authentic, quality-assured supply.</p></article>
      <article class="tl-step"><h3>Store</h3><p>Goods land at our Malé warehouse with full inventory control and cold-chain handling for chilled lines.</p></article>
      <article class="tl-step"><h3>Distribute</h3><p>Orders are picked, packed and dispatched to retailers and sub-distributors across the atolls.</p></article>
      <article class="tl-step"><h3>Replenish</h3><p>We monitor movement and restock fast — so your shelves never run dry and sales never stall.</p></article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- QUALITY / CERT BAND -->
<section class="section bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="split split--reverse">
      <div class="split__media"><img src="/placeholder.jpg" alt="Quality inspection of food products" loading="lazy"></div>
      <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Certified for confidence</span>
        <h2>Quality first, always</h2>
        <p>Food safety isn't negotiable. We work to recognised international standards across handling, storage and distribution — so retailers and customers can trust every product that carries our delivery.</p>
        <ul class="flow" style="margin-top:18px">
          <li style="display:flex;gap:12px"><span style="color:var(--green);font-weight:800">✓</span> Temperature-controlled storage for dairy and chilled goods</li>
          <li style="display:flex;gap:12px"><span style="color:var(--green);font-weight:800">✓</span> Strict stock rotation and shelf-life management</li>
          <li style="display:flex;gap:12px"><span style="color:var(--green);font-weight:800">✓</span> Traceable sourcing from approved manufacturers</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="contact.html" class="btn btn--primary mt-4">Talk to Our Team</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section bg-cream">
  <div class="container"><div class="cta-band">
    <h2>Let's build dependable supply together</h2>
    <p>Whether you run a single shop or a chain of stores, we'll keep your shelves stocked with the brands customers ask for.</p>
    <div class="btns"><a href="contact.html" class="btn btn--gold btn--lg">Get a Quote</a><a href="products.html" class="btn btn--on-dark btn--lg">View Products</a></div>
  </div></div>
</section>

</main>
</Layout>
